# {{project_name}}

{{project_name}} is a FastAPI full-stack project, scaffolded by [dev-ready](https://github.com/MoofonLi/dev-ready) on top of [fastapi/full-stack-fastapi-template](https://github.com/fastapi/full-stack-fastapi-template): a FastAPI + SQLModel + PostgreSQL backend and a React + TypeScript + Vite frontend, wired together with Docker Compose.

## Stack

- **Backend**: FastAPI, SQLModel, PostgreSQL, Pydantic — `backend/`
- **Frontend**: React, TypeScript, Vite — `frontend/`
- **Infra**: Docker Compose, Traefik reverse proxy — `compose.yml`

## Commands

- `docker compose up -d` — start the full stack (backend, frontend, database, proxy)
- `docker compose watch` — start with live reload for local development
- `docker compose down` — stop the stack
- Backend only: `cd backend && uv run fastapi dev app/main.py`
- Frontend only: `cd frontend && npm install && npm run dev`
- Backend tests: `cd backend && bash scripts/test.sh`

## Repo layout

- `backend/` — FastAPI application, SQLModel models, Alembic migrations
- `frontend/` — React application
- `compose.yml` — local development orchestration (`compose.override.yml` adds the local-dev overrides)
- `docs/` — design docs for this project, if generated with the docs overlay

